      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIOUX WARRIOR (2) did some work and faded at his latest appearance at Melton but there was merit in his other two efforts this time including a second at Kilmore two back. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and he is race fit now so worth another chance. SNICKERS EXPRESS (4) finished sixth last start at this circuit and distance but was less than 5 metres off the winner after a good third from the back row at this venue the run prior. On his best form he is good enough to take this out. METRO SWISH NZ (3) produced another good effort last time out when third from the back row at this venue, her third placing from her last four outings. Draws well and could break through. BUCKLES FOR BERRY (6) returns to the front row after finishing fifth at Kilmore last time out. Respect.",
